ptural, show-stopping shapes. Whatever you had in mind (and even a few things you didn't), there's every chance the one is already hanging here in Cheshire, waiting for you.</p>\n</div></section>"}, "elements": []}], "isInner": false}, {"id": "994cffd", "elType": "container", "settings": {"content_width": "full", "width": {"unit": "%", "size": 100, "sizes": []}, "padding": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "margin": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "flex_gap": {"unit": "px", "size": 0, "sizes": [], "column": "0", "row": "0"}, "flex_direction": "column"}, "elements": [{"id": "65e762f", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "html", "settings": {"html": "<section class=\"section band-ivory2\"><div class=\"container split\">\n<div class=\"framed reveal\"><img alt=\"Sophia Tolli romantic lace wedding gown with beaded bodice - designer wedding dresses at Wife To Be, Chester &amp; Cheshire\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"__WTB_BASE__/assets/sophia-tolli-2.jpg\"/></div>\n<div class=\"reveal\"><span class=\"eyebrow\">Sophia Tolli</span><h2>Softly Romantic</h2><span class=\"divider left\"></span><p>Loved the world over for gentle, flattering shapes, intricate lacework and cleverly engineered bodices. If it's timeless, feminine romance you're after, this is where many brides fall for their first favourite.</p><div class=\"card-tags\"><span class=\"tag\">Lace Detailing</span><span class=\"tag\">Fitted Bodices</span><span class=\"tag\">Romantic Shapes</span></div></div>\n</div></section>"}, "elements": []}], "isInner": false}, {"id": "02d1307", "elType": "container", "settings": {"content_width": "full", "width": {"unit": "%", "size": 100, "sizes": []}, "padding": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "margin": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "flex_gap": {"unit": "px", "size": 0, "sizes": [], "column": "0", "row": "0"}, "flex_direction": "column"}, "elements": [{"id": "096c41e", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "html", "settings": {"html": "<section class=\"section\"><div class=\"container split\">\n<div class=\"reveal\" style=\"order:2\"><span class=\"eyebrow\">Veni Infantino</span><h2>Quietly Bold</h2><span class=\"divider left\"></span><p>Considered, contemporary gowns cut from beautiful fabrics, made for the bride who wants to feel current and confident without ever tipping into fuss. Understated glamour, done properly.</p><div class=\"card-tags\"><span class=\"tag\">Statement Gowns</span><span class=\"tag\">Modern Cuts</span><span class=\"tag\">Luxury Fabrics</span></div></div>\n<div class=\"framed reveal\"><img alt=\"Veni Infantino ball gown with floral appliqu\u00e9 - contemporary designer wedding dresses at Wife To Be, Cheshire\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"__WTB_BASE__/assets/veni-2.jpg\"/></div>\n</div></section>"}, "elements": []}], "isInner": false}, {"id": "1d2cd19", "elType": "container", "settings": {"content_width": "full", "width": {"unit": "%", "size": 100, "sizes": []}, "padding": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "margin": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "flex_gap": {"unit": "px", "size": 0, "sizes": [], "column": "0", "row": "0"}, "flex_direction": "column"}, "elements": [{"id": "552099f", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "html", "settings": {"html": "<section class=\"section band-ivory2\"><div class=\"container split\">\n<div class=\"framed reveal\"><img alt=\"Phoenix Gowns pearl high-neck wedding dress with cape and feathered train - customisable designer bridal gowns at Wife To Be, Cheshire\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"__WTB_BASE__/assets/phoenix-gowns-3.webp\"/></div>\n<div class=\"reveal\"><span class=\"eyebrow\">Phoenix Gowns</span><h2>Made Around You</h2>